textAfterTable: Kristina Bradford, Louisiana Department of Education Network Team Member, recently visited Fellowship Elementary.  Shown with her are Tish Budemer, Instructional Supervisor, and Brandy Brunson, FES Principal. Melissa Mainiero, Louisiana Department of Education Network Team Member, recently visited LaSalle High School.  Shown with Melissa are Owen Gauthier, Sarah Peppers, Sara Gifford, and Cheryl Allbritton. State Superintendent John White Visits Fellowship Elementary Fellowship Elementary Principal, Brandy Brunson, teachers, staff, and students were hosts to a visit from Louisiana Superintendent of Education, John White, on Wednesday, October 24, 2012.  During the morning, Mr. White met with LaSalle Schools Superintendent, Roy Breithaupt, Supervisors, and Administrators.  Mr. White also observed Amanda Bibbens' Pre-K Classroom. Photo of Ms. Bibbens' classroom courtesy of John White, Louisiana Superintendent of Education. LaSalle Principals Attend LAP Conference Five LaSalle Parish Principals recently attended the Louisiana Association of Principals 61st Annual Conference in Baton Rouge.
